{"tid":2060843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"圖片展遍地開花 紀念勇武第一擊  今晚8點全港唱《榮光》","createTime":"2020-06-12T02:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T10:23:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef83ccf0afbd8247b3373d313623e22374a61cb9","tid":2060843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200612/KBHDBUM47RHJ7SOM5RPASV5XWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200612%2FKBHDBUM47RHJ7SOM5RPASV5XWU%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=c8ccc140\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200612%2FKBHDBUM47RHJ7SOM5RPASV5XWU%2F&h=262a95f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200612/KBHDBUM47RHJ7SOM5RPASV5XWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n圖片展遍地開花 紀念勇武第一擊 <br />\n今晚8點全港唱《榮光》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QB7KEGG5ODDSZF5KPUA2QA5JGE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQB7KEGG5ODDSZF5KPUA2QA5JGE.gif&h=c67f48e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年6.12警方向和平抗爭者施放催淚彈，成為反送中運動的轉捩點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【6.12一周年】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今日是6.12抗爭一周年，去年今日大批市民湧往金鐘立法會外集會，要求林鄭政府撤銷送中條例，警方竟在獲得不反對通知書的集會範圍施放催淚彈，港人怒火一發不可收拾，成為反送中運動的轉捩點。面對林鄭政府以限聚令打壓，民間團隊今日未能舉行集會，祈禱會亦被迫取消，民間集會團隊及網民決定遍地開花走向街頭，在各區舉辦圖片展及「和你Sing」活動，呼籲市民今日穿黑色衣物或佩飾紀念6.12。<br />\n<br />\n記者：謝明明 王春怡<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊發起「6.12遍地開花 社區展覽」，團隊昨發聲明表示，去年6.12香港人用行動抵擋惡法，開啟流水革命。。。。。。。。。。。。。。歷過的一切」。團隊呼籲港人今日6.12一周年穿黑色衣物或佩飾，參與18區街頭展覽，以及在晚上8時合唱《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5LUXW3ZOVOEIIOFLLFTESUKEAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5LUXW3ZOVOEIIOFLLFTESUKEAM.gif&h=30bb1007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣今日舉行6.12一周年活動，捍衞港人自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2B27JMB4YK2DHOJ4MCIB67UGM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI2B27JMB4YK2DHOJ4MCIB67UGM.gif&h=68de8e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰：堅守五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：6.12下令放TG 陶輝死撐正確<br />\n<br />\n團隊並公。。。。。。。。。。。。。暴資訊，至晚上8時相關區議員會與大家一起唱《願榮光歸香港》。另有網民發起今晚於馬鞍山新港城中庭和旺角舉辦「和你Sing」活動，齊唱《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n集會備。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n「林鄭繼續借疫情收窄港人集會嘅權利，令到我哋無辦法走出嚟，已經無得沮喪，而係覺得有種無處宣洩嘅憤怒」。他呼。。。。。。。。。五大訴求，「我哋頂住咗送中條例，但另一條可以送中嘅國安法又嚟到，我哋要堅守五大訴求繼續落去，但希望大家記住喺（抗爭）運動裏面不受傷、不被捕、不流血，大家要保重自己。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GV5KNWYOP3IWRCMYRLRDQIEKRU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGV5KNWYOP3IWRCMYRLRDQIEKRU.gif&h=d32d2093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣聲援 展千封家書<br />\n<br />\n另外，在台灣支援香港流亡青年的團隊「與理同暴」亦與台灣立法院等組織，今日6.12一周年合辦「千里送家書」展覽，展出過千封來自港人從香港寄。。。。。。。。。。。。的香港抗爭者分享等。"},{"pid":"cb8b41f6af4aac1f7d23412a81bf4660deced47c","tid":2060843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"留夕"},{"pid":"d5dc546f6b88a04087344eb55eb868b6cbb0302d","tid":2060843,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c1b3c2e489f9230c534d8a8e095ce8dc93796e","tid":2060843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"我應該去港島"},{"pid":"fcca08bd8bcb6e701810954a7ab56f5cb9d1cbbe","tid":2060843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"今日係 2020-06-12<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-13 蘋果日報 頭條<br />\n<br />\n頭條<br />\n<br />\n反惡法 二次佔中<br />\n暴政向我們開槍 <br />\n示威者血與汗<br />\n拉倒首日審議<br />\n警以退為進 示威者中伏 <br />\n警違法用武 多人頭中彈 <br />\n港台司機中流彈當場昏迷 <br />\n「交通意外」頻生堵道路<br />\n解放軍武裝戒備<br />\n向記者噴椒 濫權襲途人 <br />\n國際特赦組織譴責港警<br />\n連儂牆再現 快速被清走<br />\n社聯灣仔設臨時休息站<br />\n林鄭鱷魚淚下死不讓步 <br />\n湯家驊死撐 泛民轟撥火<br />\n陳智思暗示解放軍出動<br />\n國際不滿 矛頭指習<br />\n建制「潛水」傳匿安全屋 <br />\n通宵奔波保護群眾 鄺俊宇暈倒 <br />\n保安拒民主派入立法會<br />\n大律師公會再促撤草案<br />\n戰場上 千禧後面孔湧現<br />\n「補水」大學生：自己前途自己爭取<br />\n考完試趕到 00後：唔係淨識玩抖音<br />\n中資女員工「怯都要上」<br />\n何韻詩隻身阻警察進逼示威者<br />\n廢墟攝影師無限期奮戰<br />\n教協發動本周全港罷課<br />\n「香港問題比讀書重要」<br />\n上班族︰影響微 不介意<br />\n7前政治官員促撤惡法<br />\n曾俊華促警方理性執勤<br />\n明光社籲官憑良心辭職<br />\n美日內推法案制裁港官 <br />\n多國續示威聲援港人<br />\n外媒關注警襲示威者 <br />\n僑生促台限制港警入境 <br />\n內地播反送中 NHK斷訊號 <br />\n台南港人絕食 跪謝示威者<br />\n衝擊金融 港股挫480點 <br />\n林鄭甩底 港交所酒會取消 <br />\n市民提走中資億元表不滿<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/archive/index/20190613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Farchive%2Findex%2F20190613&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0tUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=9c68518e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Farchive%2Findex%2F20190613&h=ea2227c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/archive/index/20190613</a>"},{"pid":"dc7746170d3e322468e424c8313dbd6b474c03d9","tid":2060843,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6eebb5bd61d443099d8c6daeb6ae017b4de3247","tid":2060843,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2467bf1c4e649a1d31966bb137ff67339bf